    <etym xml:lang="ru">Деепричастная форма от глагола %ibær%i- ‘хотеть’, сохранившегося в форме
            <ref type="xr" target="#entry_bællyn"/> q. v. Таким образом, <mentioned xml:lang="os"
                ><lang/><w>bærgæ</w></mentioned> и по образованию и по значению представляет полную
        аналогию с <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/><w>хотя</w></mentioned> (деепричастие от
            <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/><w>хотеть</w></mentioned>); ср. для семантики также
            <mentioned xml:lang="de"
            ><lang/><w>wohl</w><gloss><q>весьма</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="de"
                    ><w/><gloss><q>конечно</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="de"
                ><w>wiewohl</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="de"
                    ><w>obwohl</w><gloss><q>хотя</q></gloss></mentioned>, (от <mentioned
            xml:lang="de"><lang/><w>wollen</w><gloss><q>хотеть</q></gloss></mentioned>). См. <ref
            type="xr" target="#entry_bar"/>.</etym>
    <etym xml:lang="en">A converb of the verb %ibær%i- ‘want’ which is found in <ref type="xr"
            target="#entry_bællyn"/> q. v. Thus, <mentioned xml:lang="os"
            ><lang/><w>bærgæ</w></mentioned> and represents a full analogy by its derivation and its
        meaning with <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/><w>xotya</w></mentioned> (a converb of the verb
            <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/><w>xotet'</w><gloss><q>want</q></gloss></mentioned>);
        for semantics cf. also <mentioned xml:lang="de"
            ><lang/><w>wohl</w><gloss><q>very</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="de"
                    ><w/><gloss><q>of course</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="de"
                ><w>wiewohl</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="de"
                    ><w>obwohl</w><gloss><q>though</q></gloss></mentioned>, (from <mentioned
            xml:lang="de"><lang/><w>wollen</w><gloss><q>want</q></gloss></mentioned>). See <ref
            type="xr" target="#entry_bar"/>.</etym>
